flowchart TD
    A[Start: synthesis conclusions] --> B[Run sensitivity checks on assumptions]
    B --> C[Test alternative explanations]
    C --> D[Assess robustness across segments]
    D --> E[Replicate findings with a second angle]
    E --> F[Red-team objections and responses]
    F --> G[Revise synthesis claims when needed]
    G --> H[Write validation.md]
    H --> I[Save validation queries, charts, and CSV outputs]
    I --> J[Checkpoint: proceed to Data Storytelling?]
